com.desafio.ponto.service.base

Class RegistroPontoLocalServiceBaseImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.liferay.portal.kernel.service.BaseLocalServiceImpl
      • com.desafio.ponto.service.base.RegistroPontoLocalServiceBaseImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RegistroPontoLocalService, com.liferay.portal.kernel.module.framework.service.IdentifiableOSGiService, com.liferay.portal.kernel.service.BaseLocalService
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RegistroPontoLocalServiceImpl

    @ProviderType
public abstract class RegistroPontoLocalServiceBaseImpl
extends com.liferay.portal.kernel.service.BaseLocalServiceImpl
implements RegistroPontoLocalService, com.liferay.portal.kernel.module.framework.service.IdentifiableOSGiService
    Provides the base implementation for the registro ponto local service.

    This implementation exists only as a container for the default service methods generated by ServiceBuilder. All custom service methods should be put in RegistroPontoLocalServiceImpl.

    Author:
    Peterson Morais
    See Also:
    RegistroPontoLocalServiceImpl, RegistroPontoLocalServiceUtil
